Title: In the footsteps of Pereira
DateModified: '2019-02-18'
DatePublished: '2019-02-18'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/in-the-footsteps-of-pereira
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Veronica Crocitti
AuthorCountry: Italy
Text: "Following step by step Pereira\u2019s literary history, I\u2019d like to mark\
  \ a particular itinerary from Lisbon to Porto (Lisbon-Sintra-Coimbra-Porto). \n\u201C\
  Sostiene Pereira\u201D is an italian novel written by Antonio Tabucchi in 1994.\
  \ It has been widely translated and adapted to film, garnering major European awards.\
  \ The protagonist is a portuguese who edits the culture pages of a second-rate evening\
  \ paper in 1938 Lisbon, under the dictatorship of Salazar.\nMy project \u201CIn\
  \ the footstep by Pereira\u201D would to run throught Pereira\u2019s events and\
  \ places."
